Alchemy Sciences


ALCHEMY SCIENCES™ – A MELIOR INNOVATION
Alchemy Sciences, Inc. (Alchemy), a Melior Innovations Company, is focused on significantly increasing the recovery of oil in unconventional and conventional reservoirs. By implementing a novel multi-disciplinary approach, Alchemy has established a business model to deliver a transformative solution, aimed at materially impacting asset economics.





