ALCHEMY SCIENCES, INC. $22,000 Financing
ALCHEMY SCIENCES, INC. just submitted form D announcing $22,000 equity financing.  This is a new filing. ALCHEMY SCIENCES, INC. was able to sell $14,608. That is 66% of the round of financing. The total private offering amount was $22,000. The financing was made by 59 investors. Minimal accepted investment was $0. The financing document was filed on 2016-11-23. ALCHEMY SCIENCES, INC. is based in  6002 ROGERDALE ROAD SUITE 175  HOUSTON 77072. The firm's business is Other Technology. The firm's revenue range is Decline to Disclose. The form was signed by  MARK LAND.





